query:
SELECT epa.*, e.firstName, e.lastName, p.name as projectName 
FROM employeeProjectAssignments epa
JOIN employees e ON epa.employeeId = e.id
JOIN projects p ON epa.projectId = p.id
WHERE p.name LIKE '%Raportowanie%'
LIMIT 10
